  "description": "This is a large, roomy and powerful side-by-side refrigerator. The total volume of 460 liters is enough to store food for a large family, 4-5 people. The capacious refrigerating chamber with a volume of 271 liters is equipped with 4 shelves and 2 drawers. 3 auxiliary stands are hung on the door. The freezer compartment has a similar device, which has a volume of 189 liters. The refrigeration circuit uses two heat exchangers at once, which guarantees precise adjustment and high reliability of the cooling system. The Midea MDRS 619 FGF46 refrigerator has the No Frost function, which automatically defrosts both working chambers. The model is equipped with an external screen with a convenient touch unit. If necessary, access to the settings panel can be blocked. This refrigeration unit is equipped with zones of humidity and freshness, the microclimate of which can be adjusted to the storage of certain products. The bright LED backlight makes it easy to find what you need quickly. When loading fresh food into the freezer, you can turn on the quick freeze function. In this case, the freshness will quickly freeze without prejudice to those products that were already in the working chamber.",
